pageTitle: Deadline for Murray Wise Foundation ag scholarships set for March 31 | Hoards Dairyman
TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {8600=Students preparing for careers in agriculture have until March 31 to apply for scholarships through the Murray Wise Associates Foundation. "The news is full of stories about the challenges faced by students meeting the cost of a quality education, and we had a record number of applicants a year ago.
